text: Alejandro Echaniz Partida (born 7 September 1942) is a Mexican wrestler. He competed in two events at the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1942 births Category:Living people Category:Mexican male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Mexico Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
